<i>noun</i>: 호색 [호ː색] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>호색 [호ː색]</dt><br>
<dd>lust; lewdness</dd><br>
<dd>남자가 여자와 육체적 관계를 맺는 것을 몹시 좋아하고 밝힘.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a man is extremely interested in and enjoys having a sexual relationship with a woman.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>